_sText:
Here is a fun AIM map... This map is aiming being very aim-based! (lol =P) What i mean with that is: 
1) it is the meaning that you hold the line and just move around in your own end, but if you want, you can rush across the open space.
2) There is only 2 guns per spawn point, so don't use your ammo up to quickly!!

Some facts:

Textures: Dev, or ag as some call them.
Weapons: lots of P90, 2 MP5, 2 UMP, 1 Galil, 1 Famas, and some nades.
Secrets: Yes, there is 2 scouts "hidden" some where in the map. 
Nav file: Of course :)


Enjoy the map. :)

-Twix'ed out
